{"type":null,"faqId":43465,"title":"驾驶模式的使用方法","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">启动驾驶模式，在无数据网络时可使用语音指令的方式拨打电话、播放音乐功能，如语音输入“打电话给爸爸“、”播放音乐”等。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">开启驾驶模式设置中的来电/短信播报，来电话时可以语音播报同时可以语音完成接听/挂断，来短信时可自动语音提醒并进行短信内容播报。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"8966","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442399012000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10","visitedTimes":19,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"驾驶模式,使用","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}